Battera::

She looked at Perceptor. Her optics went from narrow to normal. "I do 
not seek humor at the moment. I am seeking the best group and the 
best bots to aid me on my endevour to kill and destroy all the 
maximals. I thought.....You, would be the one best qualified to help 
me. I am still wishing that were so." She turned her head away from 
then and let out a long, soft sigh. Showing she was getting bored if 
nothing else. "Pray tell me who your leader is? Perhaps I could come 
back later and make an appointment?"
